"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Pozdravljeni,\n"
"\n"
"upamo, da ste zadovoljni z eventyay kot sistemom za CfP vašega dogodka.\n"
"Te povezave bodo morda koristne v prihodnjih dneh in tednih:\n"
"\n"
"- Nadzorna plošča vašega dogodka: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- Seznam predlogov: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Urejevalnik urnika: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"Če vam kaj manjka, nas kontaktirajte prek naše spletne strani na "
"eventyay.com.\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"just writing you to let you know that your Call for Participation is now\n"
"closed. Here is a list of links that should be useful in the next days:\n"
"\n"
"- You’ll find a list of all your {submission_count} proposals here:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- You can add reviewers here:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- You can review proposals here:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- And create your schedule here, once you have accepted proposals:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"
msgstr ""
"Pozdravljeni,\n"
"\n"
"pišem vam, da vas obvestim, da je vaš Poziv k sodelovanju zdaj\n"
"zaključen. Tukaj je seznam povezav, ki bodo v naslednjih dneh uporabne:\n"
"\n"
"- Seznam vseh vaših predlogov {submission_count} najdete tukaj:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- Tukaj lahko dodate recenzente:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- Predloge lahko ocenite tukaj:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- Ko boste predloge sprejeli, lahko tukaj ustvarite svoj urnik:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"congratulations, your event is over! Hopefully it went well. Here are some\n"
"statistics you might find interesting:\n"
"\n"
"- You had {submission_count} proposals,\n"
"- Of which you selected {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- The reviewers wrote {review_count} reviews.\n"
"- You released {schedule_count} schedules in total.\n"
"- Over the course of the event, you sent {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"Pozdravljeni,\n"
"\n"
"čitamo, vaš dogodek je zaključen! Upamo, da je potekal dobro. Tukaj je "
"nekaj\n"
"statistik, ki bi vas morda zanimale:\n"
"\n"
"- Imeli ste {submission_count} predlogov,\n"
"- od tega ste izbrali {talk_count} sej.\n"
"- Recenzenti so napisali {review_count} ocen.\n"
"- Skupaj ste objavili {schedule_count} različic urnika.\n"
"- V času dogodka ste poslali {mail_count} sporočil.\n"
"\n"
"Če vam kaj manjka, nas kontaktirajte prek naše spletne strani na "
"eventyay.com.\n"

