#: cfp/flow.py:501
msgid "That’s it about your proposal! We now just need a way to contact you."
msgstr ""
"To je vse o vašem predlogu! Sedaj potrebujemo samo še način, da vas "
"kontaktiramo."

#: cfp/flow.py:506
msgid ""
"To create your proposal, you need an account on this page. This not only "
"gives us a way to contact you, it also gives you the possibility to edit "
"your proposal or to view its current state."
msgstr ""
"Da ustvarite svoj predlog, potrebujete račun na tej strani. To nam bo "
"omogočilo, da vas kontaktiramo, kot tudi dalo možnost za urejanje vašega "
"predloga in pregled trenutnega stanja."

#: cfp/flow.py:549
#: eventyay_common/templates/eventyay_common/sessions/sessions.html:36
msgid "Profile"
msgstr "Profil"

#: cfp/flow.py:553
msgid "Tell us something about yourself!"
msgstr "Povejte nam nekaj o vas!"

#: cfp/flow.py:558
msgid ""
"This information will be publicly displayed next to your session - you can "
"always edit for as long as proposals are still open."
msgstr ""
"Te informacije bodo vidne javnosti poleg vaše seje - lahko pa jih naknadno "
"uredite dokler sprejemamo predloge."

#: cfp/phrases.py:7
msgid "Go to CfP"
msgstr "pojdite na KzP"

#: cfp/phrases.py:10
msgid ""
"If we know a user by this email address (who has not requested a password "
"reset in the last 24 hours), we will send you an email containing further "
"instructions. If you don’t see the email within the next minutes, check your "
"spam inbox!"
msgstr ""
"Če poznamo uporabnika s tem e-poštnim naslovom (ki ni zahteval ponastavitve "
"gesla v zadnjih 24 urah), bomo poslali e-poštno sporočilo z nadaljnjimi "
"navodili. Če ne vidite tega sporočila v naslednjih nekaj minutah, preverite "
"še neželeno pošto!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:14
msgid ""
"This link was not valid. Make sure you copied the complete URL from the "
"email and that the email is no more than 24 hours old."
msgstr ""
"Ta povezava ni veljavna. Preverite, da ste kopirali celoten URL iz e-"
"poštnega sporočila in, da sporočilo ni starejše od 24 ur."

#: cfp/phrases.py:17
msgid "Awesome! You can now log in using your new password."
msgstr "Super! Sedaj se lahko prijavite z novim geslom."

#: cfp/phrases.py:19
msgid "Your proposal has been withdrawn."
msgstr "Vaš predlog je bil umaknjen."

#: cfp/phrases.py:21
msgid ""
"Your proposal can’t be withdrawn at this time – please contact us if you "
"need to withdraw your proposal!"
msgstr ""
"Vaš predlog trenutno ne more biti umaknjen - prosimo kontaktirajte nas, če "
"morate predlog umakniti!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:23
msgid "Your session has been confirmed – we’re looking forward to seeing you!"
msgstr "Vaša seja je bila potrjena - veselimo se, da vas vidimo!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:24
msgid ""
"This proposal has already been confirmed – we’re looking forward to seeing "
"you!"
msgstr "Ta predlog je že potrjen - veselimo se, da vas vidimo!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:26
msgid ""
"This proposal cannot be confirmed at this time – please contact us if you "
"think this is an error."
msgstr ""
"Ta predlog trenutno ne more biti potrjen - prosimo kontaktirajte nas, če "
"menite da gre za napako."

#: cfp/phrases.py:28
msgid "This proposal cannot be edited anymore."
msgstr "Tega predloga ni mogoče več urejati."

#: cfp/phrases.py:30 cfp/phrases.py:53
msgid "Speaker email"
msgstr "E-poštni naslov govorca"

#: cfp/phrases.py:31 cfp/phrases.py:54
#, python-brace-format
msgid "{speaker} invites you to join their session!"
msgstr "{speaker} vas vabi, da se pridružite njihovi seji!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:33 cfp/phrases.py:56
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi!\n"
"\n"
"I’d like to invite you to be a speaker in the session\n"
"\n"
"  “{title}”\n"
"\n"
"at {event}. Please follow this link to join:\n"
"\n"
"  {url}\n"
"\n"
"I’m looking forward to it!\n"
"{speaker}"
msgstr ""
"Pozdravljeni!\n"
"\n"
"Vabim vas, da ste govorec na seji\n"
"\n"
"  “{title}”\n"
"\n"
"na {event}. Prosimo sledite tej povezavi, da se pridružite:\n"
"\n"
"  {url}\n"
"\n"
"Se že veselim!\n"
"{speaker}"

#: cfp/phrases.py:46
msgid "Please provide a valid email address."
msgstr "Prosimo vnesite veljaven e-poštni naslov."

#: cfp/phrases.py:47
msgid "The invitation was sent!"
msgstr "Povabilo je bilo poslano!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:48
msgid "You are now part of this proposal! Please fill in your profile below."
msgstr "Zdaj ste del tega predloga! Prosimo dopolnite svoj profil spodaj."

#: cfp/phrases.py:51
msgid ""
"We are experiencing difficulties when sending mails, but your session was "
"submitted successfully!"
msgstr ""
"Trenutno imamo težave s pošiljanjem e-poštnih sporočil, vendar vaša seja je "
"bila kljub temu uspešno oddana!"

#: cfp/phrases.py:69 orga/views/cfp.py:343
msgid "Custom fields"
msgstr "Polja po meri"

#: cfp/templates/cfp/event/cfp.html:31
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can enter proposals until %(deadline)s (%(timezone)s), %(until_string)s "
"from now."
msgstr ""
"Seje lahko vnesete do %(deadline)s (%(timezone)s), %(until_string)s od zdaj."

