msgid ""
"If you lose access to your devices, you can use one of the following keys to "
"log in. We recommend to store them in a safe place, e.g. printed out or in a "
"password manager. Every token can be used at most once."
msgstr ""
"Če izgubite dostop do svojih naprav, lahko za prijavo uporabite enega od "
"naslednjih ključev. Priporočamo, da jih shranite na varno mesto, npr. "
"natisnjene ali v upravitelju gesel. Vsak žeton je mogoče uporabiti največ "
"enkrat."

